  <summary date="2021-02-24T19:12:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Clarifying Law Around Insurance of Marijuana Act or the CLAIM Act 

This bill generally provides a safe harbor from penalties or other adverse agency action for insurance companies that provide services to cannabis-related businesses in jurisdictions where such activity is legal.

The Government Accountability Office must report on barriers to marketplace entry for minority-owned and women-owned cannabis-related businesses.</summary>
